    "The Bulk SMS Add-On is a simple yet powerful communication tool that allows you to send instant text messages directly from within your system. Designed to improve internal and external communication, it enables businesses to quickly reach employees, clients, or entire contact groups without the need for external platforms.": "散发短信附加程序是一个简单而强大的通信工具,可以让您直接从系统中发送即时短信.它旨在改善内部和外部通信,使企业能够快速接触员工,客户或整个联系人群,而不需要外部平台.",
    "Configure Your SMS Gateway with Ease": "轻松配置您的SMS网关",
    "The Bulk SMS Add-On makes it incredibly easy to connect your system with your SMS service. With just a few details like username and password, you`re ready to start sending messages directly from your platform.": "通过大量短信附加功能,您可以非常轻松地将系统与短信服务连接起来.只需使用用户名和密码等一些细节,您就可以从平台直接开始发送消息.",
    "Build and Manage Your Contact Base Effortlessly": "轻松建立和管理您的联系人群",
    "Keeping your contact list up to date is crucial for effective communication, and this add-on makes it simple. Add individuals with full details or import entire lists in a few clicks. Whether you`re targeting a small group or a broad audience, your contact data stays organized, accessible, and ready whenever you need to send a message.": "保持联系人列表的更新对于有效的沟通至关重要,而这个附加功能使其变得简单. 通过几次点击添加完整的详细信息或导入整个列表. 无论您是针对小群体还是广大受众,您的联系人数据都保持有组织,可访问,并且随时准备好发送消息.",
    "Create Targeted Groups for Smarter Messaging": "创建目标群组以更智能地发送信息",
    "Group messaging has never been easier. You can create and manage contact groups based on your communication needs, perfect for departments, client segments, or events. Instead of sending messages one by one, group messaging helps you reach the right audience quickly and consistently, saving time and boosting productivity.": "群组消息传递从来没有那么容易. 您可以根据您的沟通需求创建和管理联系人群, 非常适合各部门,客户群或事件. 群组消息传递不仅仅是单独发送消息, 更能帮助您快速,一致地接触到合适的受众, 节省时间,提高生产力.",
    "Send Powerful Messages That Get Delivered": "传递有力信息,得到传递",
    "From urgent alerts to regular updates, the Bulk SMS Add-On helps you get your message across instantly. Send to one person or hundreds with the same ease. Messages are sent reliably, tracked automatically, and organized neatly for future reference. It`s fast, effective, and built to keep your communication on point.": "从紧急警报到定期更新,大量短信附加功能可以帮助您立即传递您的信息. 轻松地发送给一个人或数百人. 消息可靠地发送,自动跟踪,并整齐地组织以供将来参考. 它快速,有效,并旨在保持您的通信."
